## Accessibility & Performance
- **Contrast:** High-contrast text tokens (`--text-dark` on light, `--text-on-dark` on dark).
- **Navigation:** ARIA labels on all icon-only buttons (`menu-toggle`, `slider-arrow`).
- **Semantic HTML:** Strict usage of `<header>`, `<main>`, `<section>`, `<article>`, and `<footer>` for screen reader clarity.
- **Performance:** Imagery is primarily in `.webp` format for faster loading; critical CSS is optimized for top-of-page rendering.
